  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dde\u0d9b\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dbb \u0da7\u0ddd\u0d9a\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dba\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Opposition to giving the token before health",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A protest has started near the Galle Fort petrol station this morning (01) and security forces have tightened security in the area.",
        "A group of people who had previously obtained tokens are protesting at the place, saying that doctors or anyone else claiming to be essential services will not be allowed to buy fuel until they are given fuel.",
        "The incident took place at a cooperative petrol station near the old fort gate of Galle Fort. A group of people who had previously obtained tokens from the fuel queue are protesting by sitting on the road at that place and they are not allowing any other vehicle to get fuel.",
        "Cipetco has sent a fuel bowser to the petrol station today (01) to obtain fuel for doctors and other health workers, government documents confirm.",
        "Even so, the people who got the tokens say that after giving fuel to them, they should give fuel to the doctors and other health workers."
      ],
